      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It's in absolutely stunning shape\u2014basically looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it's looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Everything is pristine, inside and out. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it!",
