    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a collector-grade example of the iconic wide-body 996.2. The M96 3.6L flat-six engine delivers linear power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle, benefiting from a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. This C4S utilizes a viscous coupling all-wheel-drive system and the reinforced chassis of the Turbo variant, ensuring superior torsional rigidity and lateral grip. The factory suspension remains taut, paired with 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management during deceleration. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like finish with no rock chips or swirl marks, while the interior leather bolsters remain firm and free of UV-related fatigue. A mechanically transparent, turnkey specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
