    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Porsche 718 Cayman is a pristine, collector-grade example that presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The Guards Red paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish thanks to a professional ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time capsule' condition, with the black leather upholstery still firm and retaining its original factory scent. Every surface, from the Alcantara headliner to the precision-stitched dashboard, is free of wear or sunlight exposure. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been pampered with a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by Porsche-certified technicians. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen rain or snow. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that feels, looks, and drives like a brand-new vehicle.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
